Soundtrack
The score for Couples Retreat was composed and produced by Oscar-winner A.R.
Rahman and recorded in the summer of 2009 with the Hollywood Studio Symphony at the Sony Scoring Stage.
The film marks the Hollywood debut for Rahman.
A soundtrack album will be released by Relativity Music Group.
