Reception
The film has received negative reviews.
According to Metacritic, which assigns a normalized rating out of 100 top reviews from mainstream critics, the film has a score of 24 based on 25 reviews.
Rotten Tomatoes reports that 13% of critics gave the film a positive review, based upon a sample of 100, with an average score of 3.7 out of 10.
Despite the critical reception, it was a box office success, ranking #1.
